FBIS4-42833 "drweu111_b_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-111 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 BENELUX COUNTRIES Belgium Radio Ordered To Give Air Time to Right-Wing Parties Radio Ordered To Give Air Time to Right-Wing Parties LD0806164094 Brussels La Une Radio Network in French 1600 GMT 8 Jun 94 LD0806164094 Brussels La Une Radio Network French BFN [Excerpt] Today the Appeals Court confirmed the decision of the ruling judge, ordering the RTBF to give the extreme right parties and the National Front access to the RTBF electoral slots. The Court has therefore rejected the arguments of the RTBF. [passage omitted]
